{"tid":2192140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大龍鳳僅揪出11個案 比率0.0025%","createTime":"2020-09-07T02:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T03:01:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2521e77fc91757c441b7f87f00e583f03ccd8af1","tid":2192140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/2WQQPOCOQJD5HKFEVKO2DIWUCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2F2WQQPOCOQJD5HKFEVKO2DIWUCU%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=049ab945\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2F2WQQPOCOQJD5HKFEVKO2DIWUCU%2F&h=5921ddab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/2WQQPOCOQJD5HKFEVKO2DIWUCU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n大龍鳳僅揪出11個案 比率0.0025%<br />\n<br />\n■政府指內地已派570人來港支援檢測；圖為內地核酸檢測支援隊代表日前出席歡迎座談會。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】普及社區檢測計劃截至周六完成了約43.9萬個樣本，而截止周六午夜，衞生防護中心僅錄得11宗個案經計劃發現，比率僅0.0025%。立法會議員張超雄認為，計劃效益低，應集中資源為院舍員工等高危群組化驗，「應該每七日驗一次」。呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超則指，檢測量滯後，待幾日才有檢測結果，減低切斷傳播鏈的效用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員促集中高危群組<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥曾預計全港有1,500隱形患者，希望透過全民檢測找到，但目前數字證明計劃不似預期。衞生署傳染病處主任張竹君稱，計劃成效需待完成後才能判斷，若檢出數字較低，或代表社區中隱形個案不多。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員張超雄認為，測出陽性的比例偏低，計劃成效非常差，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨日公佈的三名確診者同於9月2日接受全民檢測，9月4日才有結果，5日才確診。呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超表示，全民檢測採樣加快，但檢測量滯後，或要等數日才有結果，減低切斷傳播鏈的效用，「發現嘅陽性個案傳播可能只剩番三至四日，如果要兩至三日先有報告，將阻截傳播鏈嘅功能大打折扣」，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸累計570人已來港<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始昨於無綫節目《講清講楚》表示，中央支援隊昨再派出百多人來港，累計有570名成員，。。。。。"},{"pid":"82767183c64bf6a716d62705a247dafa258c3445","tid":2192140,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"今次又浪費多少個億？"},{"pid":"ba6937085adc9cb2b209e8c5c08cec98bc6ff8bc","tid":2192140,"uid":118082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82767183c64bf6a716d62705a247dafa258c3445","tid":2192140,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"今次又浪費多少個億？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"15-20億<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19c397e9af68221f7b8c85c5d80167d832cfc3f","tid":2192140,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba6937085adc9cb2b209e8c5c08cec98bc6ff8bc","tid":2192140,"uid":118082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82767183c64bf6a716d62705a247dafa258c3445","tid":2192140,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"今次又浪費多少個億？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"15-20億<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:56:02.000Z","msg":"不肯全民派錢<br />\n<br />\n但可以浪費15-20億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda3ae599d5a9119f183b3b78a1d582ede68960c","tid":2192140,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由佢確診算數啦"},{"pid":"e0f251b387db760e67c991e9f1bcc31dbf1bced4","tid":2192140,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"再次證明要封關<br />\n當初豁免船員同機組人員係全心播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}